snippet.title: Super Voxel World Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Available at https://bng.itch.io/super-voxel-world

Super Voxel World is a multiplayer sandbox game. Build worlds, add gameplay, and share them with others online. Currently available for PC in Early Access.
